6//\NOTE: This file is part of an attempt to replace version specific opcode files.
7// It works with internal indexes and maps version hex values to them. Do not
8// use or work with this file unless you are able to understand what is
9// happening here ;)
10
11#pragma once
12
13#include <cstdint>
14#include <string>
15#include <map>
16
17#define MAX_VERSION_INDEX 5
18
19enum class OpcodeDevelopmentState
20{
21 Okay,
22 NotUsed,
23 Unchecked
24};
25
26struct MultiversionOpcodeTable
27{
28 uint32_t versionFlag;
29 std::string name;
30 OpcodeDevelopmentState state;
31 uint16_t hexValues[MAX_VERSION_INDEX];
32};
